commit.message: README: Clarify install target and spell the numbers
Rename pam.d from google-auth to gauth

Pass input config via fd instead of file

Pass input config via fd instead of reading it directly from the file.
This makes it possible for program to run with reduced privileges,
and therefore being unable to read the original file.
Make buffer length calculations more verbatim
Support write-only secret store via setuid gauthctl
Trivial wrappers to enable and disable OTP via gauth
